<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="es">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Redirecting...</title>
    <link rel="canonical" href="https://inaqui.me/es">
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="es" href="https://inaqui.me/es">
    <link rel="alternate" hreflang="en" href="https://inaqui.me/en">
</head>
<body>
    <p>Redirigiendo... Si no eres redirigido automáticamente, elige tu idioma:</p>
    <ul>
        <li><a href="/es">Español</a></li>
        <li><a href="/en">English</a></li>
    </ul>
    <script>
        const userLang = navigator.language || "es";
        if (userLang.startsWith("es")) {
            window.location.href = "/es";
        } else {
            window.location.href = "/en";
        }
    </script>
</body>
</html>
